{"tid":757430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【放蛇拉黑的】警表露身份司機拒停車　金鐘「挾持」到北角始被截","createTime":"2018-07-27T00:31:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T03:13:52.000Z","uid":55851,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"c8a957e9e212dd8338f92c1f54bd0d3ef268fc91","tid":757430,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T00:31:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/083101_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F083101_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=e4ac2bdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方中區警區軍裝巡邏小隊人員，今日凌晨時份在中環蘭桂坊進行打擊的士濫收車資行動。凌晨約3時，1名男警長被派往「放蛇」，假扮乘客由蘭桂坊上車前往金鐘港島香格里拉酒店。據知，有人獅子張大口，開價150元車資；但實際按錶收費，只需約40元。<br />\n<br />\n待的士駛到目的地時，司機收取了150元，車上「乘客」隨即表露警員身份，並宣示要作出拘捕行動。有人得悉「中伏」，再加上見到車外早有「重兵」恭候，竟二話不說，載著男警長連人帶車一起「踩大油」逃走。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息稱，該的士挾著警長，沿東區走廊加速駛至柴灣，在環翠邨對開迴旋處再折返，直至北角興發街與歌頓街交界時，終被4輛警車前後包抄，司機見狀只好停車，惟有人仍拒絕落車。在警方多次示意「武力指示」後，的士司機最終肯合作，自行落車，並無反抗。<br />\n<br />\n據知期間的士除超速外，亦多次衝燈及越過雙白線。的士上的放蛇男警長，因暈眩不適須送院治理。警方終以涉嫌「濫收車資」、「拒捕」及「瘋狂駕駛」，將該名60歲姓何男司機拘捕，消息稱，有人早有「前科」，於2015年被控以「濫收車資」罪名。<br />\n<br />\n此外，警方事後檢走的士司機之的士證，並與一張香格里拉的酒店房卡一併帶署作為證物。有警員透露，由於黑的士司機素來蠱惑，故警員要帶備「酒店房卡」，以待的士司機檢查，確定為「住客」後始開天殺價，否則會惹來懷疑，令他們不敢露出狼相。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/突發/215594/放蛇拉黑的-警表露身份司機拒停車-金鐘-挾持-到北角始被截?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC%2F215594%2F%E6%94%BE%E8%9B%87%E6%8B%89%E9%BB%91%E7%9A%84-%E8%AD%A6%E8%A1%A8%E9%9C%B2%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E6%8B%92%E5%81%9C%E8%BB%8A-%E9%87%91%E9%90%98-%E6%8C%BE%E6%8C%81-%E5%88%B0%E5%8C%97%E8%A7%92%E5%A7%8B%E8%A2%AB%E6%88%AA%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost_link%26utm_campaign%3Dmama&d=UAQ9pE%2FGVdgdJKmfP0crvtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=8979641e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/突發/215594/放蛇拉黑的-警表露身份司機拒停車-金鐘-挾持-到北角始被截?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama</a>"},{"pid":"d12792461fe99c2440e4495e04594a561860acbe","tid":757430,"uid":38177,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T00:45:54.000Z","msg":"比人挾封既警長<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢喺架的士到一定嚇到瀨屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c994ebc9d447f0c611c0034cb2772009dbb0b452","tid":757430,"uid":55851,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T00:47:14.000Z","msg":"厲害了，我的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68005790c9e0e4748c8af4fe98c08c75752e9327","tid":757430,"uid":25858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d12792461fe99c2440e4495e04594a561860acbe","tid":757430,"uid":38177,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T00:45:54.000Z","msg":"比人挾封既警長<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢喺架的士到一定嚇到瀨屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T00:49:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2657f21e75066ed2ab0c398ee451014d90260011","tid":757430,"uid":133223,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T00:49:54.000Z","msg":"人地係你車上面<br />\n個的士佬憑咩覺得自己會走得甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64322feabdbb980fa720feca865b8da3e1d3b6e3","tid":757430,"uid":70411,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T00:51:14.000Z","msg":"放蛇都要book香格里拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"